Download Etcher and flash into the USB
  https://etcher.balena.io/#download-etcher

Download Proxmox Virtual Environment then use Etcher and flash onto it.
  https://www.proxmox.com/en/downloads/proxmox-virtual-environment

*NOTE: Keep the password safe. When login in, the username is "root" and whatever your password is.
*NOTE: If you are connected to Ethernet/Switch and it does not detect it. Run: dhclient -v

(if everytime you boot up the server and the ip address doesn't change or stay the same)
-> Do: nano /etc/network/interfaces
  -> Change the address and gateway
     address should be changed to the ip address that was ran on the "dhclient -v"
     gateway should be changed to the default gateway aka how you access your router page
-> Ctrl X -> Y -> Enter
-> Run: systemctl restart networking

*Do this step on your actual pc and browser.
Next, access your default gateway (find it under your modem)
Go to DHCP Reservation and select your server IP and reserve it
